        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Battery Material Processing and Component Manufacturing Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Energy to establish grant programs to support, enhance, and sustain a domestic supply chain for batteries, including grants to facilities for processing, manufacturing, and recycling batteries.</p>]]>
        </text>
